{"tid":26151,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人另一半成個星期都唔聯絡一次","createTime":"2016-12-06T14:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T15:42:27.000Z","uid":55350,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a14278a1f0ed5f0e996cffcc29c462178def86c6","tid":26151,"uid":55350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"有無人自己或者另一半幾日甚至成個星期都唔搵對方？<br />\n講緊一句whatsapp都無<br />\n<br />\n我同ex拍拖三個幾月 頭一兩個月都會日日聯絡<br />\n到咗第三個月 佢無啦啦情緒好差 話做野壓力好大<br />\n突然成個星期無主動聯絡過我 間中我都係text佢幾句<br />\n態度差左好多 好惡 好似變左另一個人咁<br />\n之後一直都係咁 頂左成個月<br />\n我頂唔到 講左分開下 冷靜下<br />\n<br />\n而家大半年 都係糾纏緊 佢開頭話會改 但就變本加厲<br />\n幾日無搵過大家 我有時忍唔住問佢<br />\n叫佢搵我 佢又屌鳩我煩 講緊係用粗口鬧我<br />\n仲話因為我煩先唔搵我 唔見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n期間試過1、2個月先見1,2次 食個飯咁<br />\n但係都比人臨時放飛機過兩次<br />\n試過半個月無一句msg 兩個月無見<br />\n我生日已經唔奢想佢同我慶祝 點知連一句生日快樂都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我無咩要求 只係想佢一兩日搵我講下野<br />\n一星期見我一次<br />\n佢話以前拍拖都係成個星期唔聯絡，一個月見得一次<br />\n話我chur鳩佢 係我煩 唔信佢<br />\n佢唔鍾意覆msg就唔覆 佢唔覺自己有問題<br />\n<br />\n我從來無要求過佢比d咩我 我想同另一半聯絡 講下野咋<br />\n有無巴絲都係咁？ 係咪我要求太高？<br />\n佢口講話 我咁煩都覆我 比著其他人理都唔會理<br />\n我好辛苦 我感覺唔到佢重視過我<br />\n我就黎痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢係咪玩鳩我咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532eb954bb18ca80238543e60855437caa3aae96","tid":26151,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"出家做尼姑"},{"pid":"d043f557ab7446c985c6a7ddc43e35e37df44c2b","tid":26151,"uid":10962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"分手啱㗎喇<br />\n佢根本唔重視你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鍾意一個人點會捨得唔見呀"},{"pid":"5f158bdb16ff55b132e3a15a726ee10ae09e2b09","tid":26151,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"鬼上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9f04c0f6b5650f6dd65d0b7a6bbe1fc0f34867","tid":26151,"uid":5566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"On9 兵都不如"},{"pid":"87a5af3f8403a52bc5213f0fa3a64b9ed858a4cb","tid":26151,"uid":29065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"你地拍緊拖架原來？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁既拍拖 咪撚要啦"},{"pid":"b368937995b04c17cb7d21eef2472e5683fe1514","tid":26151,"uid":54018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"你係咪發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左熱戀期一星期見一次是常識吧<br />\n正常日日都會wtsapp<br />\n雖然我回得慢有時會吾記得覆 但都會交待下<br />\n利申:絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9545a1e2a84d84b1ba34924d32a5f591078b54a7","tid":26151,"uid":54018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左熱戀期一星期見一次是常識吧<br />\n正常日日都會wtsapp<br />\n雖然我回得慢有時會唔記得覆 但都會交待下<br />\n利申:絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3634e5b467f0be4d8366e87b3ebc6aa1b99a7c3f","tid":26151,"uid":7139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"日日都講電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48540a3da4743e92cabaefb0621104f0312cbd0","tid":26151,"uid":29280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"你確定你拍緊拖 唔係做緊兵? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放手把啦 同呢個人一齊